snippet: Marin Cilic broke through for his first Masters 1000 series title on Sunday, beating Andy Murray in the final of the Western & Southern Open and ending the Scot's 22-match winning streak....
lead_paragraph: Marin Cilic broke through for his first Masters 1000 series title on Sunday, beating Andy Murray in the final of the Western & Southern Open and ending the Scot's 22-match winning streak.

headline.print_headline: Cilic Ends Murray Win Streak in Cincinnati Final
headline.main: Cilic Ends Murray Win Streak in Cincinnati Final
